text:
Remembering the late #Liverpool legend Tommy Smith who was born OTD in 1945.

Smith played in 4 #FACup finals for Liverpool, winning in 1965 & 1974, but lost in 1971 (as captain) and again in 1977.

He passed away in 2019 aged 74.
